)\"><div class=\"group relative rounded-2xl bg-white p-2.5 shadow-[0_20px_45px_-18px_rgba(0,0,0,0.7)] ring-1 ring-amber-400/40 transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-[1.03]\"><span class=\"pointer-events-none absolute -inset-1 -z-10 rounded-3xl bg-amber-400/20 blur-md\"></span><img alt=\"Nepal Trek Agency logo\" width=\"200\" height=\"96\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto w-[150px] rounded-xl md:w-[190px]\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><p class=\"eyebrow text-amber-300\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Est. 2010 · Kathmandu, Nepal</p><h1 class=\"mt-6 font-playfair text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.05] text-snow text-balance sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[5.5rem]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Trek Beyond <span class=\"gradient-text\">the Horizon</span></h1><p class=\"mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl font-lato text-lg leading-relaxed text-snow/75 md:text-xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Expert-led Himalayan expeditions from Everest to Annapurna — guided by the people who call these mountains home.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><a class=\"btn btn-amber group\" href=\"/treks\">Explore Treks<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"btn btn-outline\" href=\"/about\">Our Story</a></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 z-10 -translate-x-1/2 text-center\" style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"font-montserrat text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-snow/60\">Scroll to discover</span><di