th d=\"M5.5 20a6.5 6.5 0 0 1 13 0\"></path><path d=\"M12 3.8V2\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-playfair text-xl font-bold text-green-900\">Local Expert Guides</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800\">Born and raised in the Himalayas, our guides know every trail, teahouse and shortcut.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-snow p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-green-700 text-amber-300 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[18deg] group-hover:scale-110\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"><path d=\"M12 3 5 6v5c0 4.4 3 8 7 10 4-2 7-5.6 7-10V6l-7-3Z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-playfair text-xl font-bold text-green-900\">Safety First</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800\">Government-certified guides, daily oximeter checks and clear emergency protocols.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-snow p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-green-700 text-amber-300 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[18deg] group-hover:scale-110\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"><path d=\"M5 20c0-9 5-14 14-14 0 9-5 14-14 14Z\"></path><path d=\"M5 20c4-4 7-6 10-7\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-playfair text-xl font-bold text-green-900\">Sustainable Trekking</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800\">Leave No Trace certified practices that protect the mountains we love.</p></div><div class=\"group rounded-3xl border border-stone-200 bg-snow p-7 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><span class=\"flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-green-700 text-amber-300 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[18deg] group-hover:scale-110\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.6\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"8\" r=\"2.6\"></circle><circle cx=\"16.5\" cy=\"9.5\" r=\"2.1\"></circle><path d=\"M4 19a5 5 0 0 1 10 0\"></path><path d=\"M14.5 19a4 4 0 0 1 5.5-3.7\"></path></svg></span><h3 class=\"mt-5 font-playfair text-xl font-bold text-green-900\">Small Groups</h3><p class=\"mt-2 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800\">Maximum 12 trekkers per group for a personal, unhurried experience.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-stone-100 section-pad\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden \"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 60 24\" class=\"absolute\" style=\"top:18%;width:60px;opacity:0.13;stroke:#4D0014;fill:none;stroke-width:2;animation:soar 30s linear infinite;animation-delay:0s\"><path d=\"M2 14 Q16 2 30 12 Q44 2 58 14\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 60 24\" class=\"absolute\" style=\"top:30%;width:42px;opacity:0.13;stroke:#4D0014;fill:none;stroke-width:2;animation:soar 42s linear infinite;animation-delay:-12s\"><path d=\"M2 14 Q16 2 30 12 Q44 2 58 14\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 60 24\" class=\"absolute\" style=\"top:12%;width:30px;opacity:0.13;stroke:#4D0014;fill:none;stroke-width:2;animation:soar 36s linear infinite;animation-delay:-24s\"><path d=\"M2 14 Q16 2 30 12 Q44 2 58 14\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"container-trek relative z-10\"><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-4 text-amber-600\">Trail Stories</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><h2 class=\"font-playfair text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-balance md:text-5xl text-green-900\">What Our Trekkers Say</h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><p class=\"mt-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-pretty text-stone-500\">Real words from real adventurers who shared the trail with us.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-warm p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-amber-400/60 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-700 font-montserrat text-sm font-bold text-snow\">IB</div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate font-dm text-lg leading-tight text-green-900\">Isabelle Bazer</p><p class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">🇫🇷<!-- --> <!-- -->France</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 \"><div class=\"flex\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"1 star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"2 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"3 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"4 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"5 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button></div></div><span class=\"rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 px-3 py-1 font-montserrat text-[11px] font-semibold text-amber-600\">Everest Base Camp</span></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800 line-clamp-4\">“<!-- -->I would like to thank Bhupendra, Dip, Sagar and all team members for your incredible enthusiasm and help in organising our two treks. You made our journey a beautiful memory, helped us discover Nepal&#x27;s people and culture. We made it to Kala Pattar — unforgettable!<!-- -->”</p><button class=\"mt-2 self-start font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600 hover:text-amber-600\">Read more</button><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-stone-200 pt-4\"><span class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">October 2023</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 text-snow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\"><path d=\"m5 12 4.5 4.5L19 7\"></path></svg></span>Verified Trek</span></div></article><article class=\"flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-warm p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-amber-400/60 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-700 font-montserrat text-sm font-bold text-snow\">JW</div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate font-dm text-lg leading-tight text-green-900\">James Whitfield</p><p class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">🇬🇧<!-- --> <!-- -->United Kingdom</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 \"><div class=\"flex\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"1 star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"2 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"3 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"4 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"5 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button></div></div><span class=\"rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 px-3 py-1 font-montserrat text-[11px] font-semibold text-amber-600\">Annapurna Circuit</span></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800 line-clamp-4\">“<!-- -->Nepal Trek Agency made my solo Annapurna Circuit dream come true. The guide, Dawa, was knowledgeable, patient, and became a true friend by day 3. Logistics were flawless — permits, teahouses, everything sorted without me lifting a finger.<!-- -->”</p><button class=\"mt-2 self-start font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600 hover:text-amber-600\">Read more</button><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-stone-200 pt-4\"><span class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">April 2024</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 text-snow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\"><path d=\"m5 12 4.5 4.5L19 7\"></path></svg></span>Verified Trek</span></div></article><article class=\"flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 bg-warm p-6 shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-amber-400/60 hover:shadow-trek\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-700 font-montserrat text-sm font-bold text-snow\">PS</div><div class=\"min-w-0\"><p class=\"truncate font-dm text-lg leading-tight text-green-900\">Priya Sharma</p><p class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">🇮🇳<!-- --> <!-- -->India</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 \"><div class=\"flex\" aria-label=\"Rated 5 out of 5\"><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"1 star\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"2 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"3 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"4 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button><button type=\"button\" disabled=\"\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 cursor-default\" aria-label=\"5 stars\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"text-amber-400\" style=\"filter:drop-shadow(0 1px 2px rgba(200,133,42,0.4))\"><path d=\"M12 2.5l2.9 5.9 6.5.9-4.7 4.6 1.1 6.5L12 17.8 6.2 20.9l1.1-6.5L2.6 9.3l6.5-.9L12 2.5Z\"></path></svg></button></div></div><span class=\"rounded-full bg-amber-400/15 px-3 py-1 font-montserrat text-[11px] font-semibold text-amber-600\">Ghorepani Poon Hill</span></div><p class=\"mt-4 flex-1 font-lato text-sm leading-relaxed text-stone-800 \">“<!-- -->My first ever trek and it couldn&#x27;t have been better. The guides were patient, encouraging, and made the whole experience feel safe and manageable. Poon Hill at sunrise was breathtaking. Highly recommend for first-timers!<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"mt-5 flex items-center justify-between border-t border-stone-200 pt-4\"><span class=\"font-montserrat text-xs text-stone-500\">March 2024</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-montserrat text-xs font-semibold text-green-600\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-600 text-snow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"11\" height=\"11\"><path d=\"m5 12 4.5 4.5L19 7\"></path></svg></span>Verified Trek</span></div></article></div><div class=\"mt-12 text-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-green group\" href=\"/reviews\">Read All Reviews<svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" class=\"transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-warm section-pad\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden \"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 60\" class=\"absolute\" style=\"top:8%;left:-20%;width:200px;opacity:0.05;fill:#4D0014;animation:soar 60s linear infinite;animation-delay:0s\"><path d=\"M40 50a20 20 0 0 1 4-39 26 26 0 0 1 49-4 18 18 0 0 1 24 17 16 16 0 0 1-3 26H40Z\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 60\" class=\"absolute\" style=\"top:22%;left:-20%;width:140px;opacity:0.05;fill:#4D0014;animation:soar 90s linear infinite;animation-delay:-20s\"><path d=\"M40 50a20 20 0 0 1 4-39 26 26 0 0 1 49-4 18 18 0 0 1 24 17 16 16 0 0 1-3 26H40Z\"></path></svg><svg viewBox=\"0 0 200 60\" class=\"absolute\" style=\"top:14%;left:-20%;width:260px;opacity:0.05;fill:#4D0014;animation:soar 75s linear infinite;animation-delay:-45s\"><path d=\"M